{"tid":1936373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"瑪麗化驗室疑調亂樣本　亞博兩新冠病毒陽性抵港者一度被錯誤放走","createTime":"2020-03-21T07:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T08:14:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b7e3d54d4d8569ccdb41cb110b239390161fc6","tid":1936373,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"醫管局在亞洲國際博覽館設立的新型冠狀病毒臨時檢測中心，昨（20日）把7個樣本交予瑪麗醫院的醫管局化驗室測試。醫管局今午（21日）表示，其中4名有病徵抵港者樣本覆檢結果與初步報告不一致，疑化驗室在化驗過程中對調4個樣本。兩名原已被放回登記居所的入境者覆檢結果呈陽性，已被送院隔離治療，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，另外兩人一直留在檢測中心等候化驗結果，其樣本經覆檢後證實對新型冠狀病毒呈陰性，兩人已得悉結果，並獲安排返回居所接受14日家居檢疫隔離。"},{"pid":"ce1faf9235fa2f8bf5a4d152a47f901c37ccbcb3","tid":1936373,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904dabf27f2d3248a8f2e77c40a8135ae8cb6cf8","tid":1936373,"uid":197669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7a8b2d297299c629071a6405838c308d4a12f3","tid":1936373,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOV1A00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOV1A00.jpg&h=38482740&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c393b5b21bca5b66f922f8e1cf28a63c12fb375","tid":1936373,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"